data.description: Breathtaking 3 YEAR OLD home! JUST LIKE NEW HOME! Welcome to your dream home, fully brick and stone two story home has so much to offer. Primary bedroom is located on the first floor with Tub shower combo, alone with double sinks. Office/Study on first floor followed by a beautiful open concept. Second floor you will find game room and 3 additional bedrooms. Besides the home there is a beautiful Lagoon/Beach located inside the community. This home is minutes from many major freeways, as well as an ever expanding array of restaurants, entertainment area, and businesses complete the perfect package. NEVER FLOODED and truly a must see!!    Seller is willing to cover expense to repaint.
